True or False?
Jean, a driver in your store is about to hop on the cut table after returning from a delivery. 
He needs to wash his hands before he starts.

True or False?
Another driver returns from their delivery within 25 minutes. Jean gives her a high five to celebrate. 

Jean now needs wash his hands.

True or False?
Jean hops over to take a phone order. He enters the order in Pulse then moves back to finish his pizza.
 Jean needs to wash his hands.

True or False?
Jean grabs some dough from the cooler to start proofing it. 

Jean needs to wash his hands before cutting a pizza?

True or False?
Jean has finished cutting the pizza! 

Jean needs to wash his hands before prepping more pepperoni for tonight's rush.

Thanks for helping Jean get a better grasp on his handwashing skills! 

(Just make sure Jean washes his hands after this high-five)
